1
00:00:58,480 --> 00:01:00,280
Shi Chen, chairman of Taichen Group,

2
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:02,120
for suspected kidnapping, murder,

3
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:03,720
and manipulating racing bets,

4
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:04,319
has been arrested by the police.

5
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:05,480
That old fox Qianye

6
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:07,220
is finally caught.

7
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,320
If murder wasn't a crime,

8
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:12,520
I'd hack him to pieces to vent my anger.

9
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:19,170
Your sister is avenged.

10
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,930
You should let go of your burden

11
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:23,780
and look toward a new life.

12
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,600
Forget it.

13
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:32,080
If you don't mind,

14
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:33,400
I can help you.

15
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:36,680
Besides,

16
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,660
your sister wouldn't want

17
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:40,530
you to live in the past forever.

18
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,410
She'd want you to move forward.

19
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:49,370
Why are you so careless?

20
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,960
It would break your sister's heart.

21
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:51,690
And it breaks

22
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:55,479
mine too.

23
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:12,240
By the way.

24
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:13,640
Well,

25
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:15,960
now that Shi Chen has been arrested,

26
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,560
what about his sponsorship?

27
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:20,260
Won't it all go down the drain?

28
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,000
It's fine.

29
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:24,010
I can figure something out.

30
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,200
No need to bother.

31
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:26,520
As for the sponsorship,

32
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,000
Master Haoran has already arranged it.

33
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,480
Luo Xin.

34
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,210
Why are you here?

35
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,850
Mr. Haoran sent me here.

36
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:34,360
You just said Gu Haoran will sponsor us.

37
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,120
Did I hear that right?

38
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,200
Yes, Miss Chen.

39
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,280
That's great.

40
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,650
Please thank him for me.

41
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,360
However,

42
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,290
Mr. Haoran has a condition.

43
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,490
What condition?

44
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:47,120
For the Dragon Country Grand Prix this time,

45
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,600
you must use the Gu Group's

46
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,810
new energy vehicles

47
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:53,010
as the official designated vehicles for the TG team.

48
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,160
That might be difficult.

49
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:59,240
Mr. Haoran hopes to use this competition

50
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:01,040
to promote new energy vehicles.

51
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,360
I agree.

52
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,280
Pleasure working with you.

53
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,810
Pleasure working with you.

54
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:12,960
When you get to this curve,

55
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,280
you need to make a special mark.

56
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,720
There's a drainage ditch here.

57
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,780
And for this curve,

58
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,480
even though the edge is like this,

59
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:18,760
Got it.

60
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,420
But this track has already...

61
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,050
Captain.

62
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,920
I have some good news for you.

63
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,760
The legendary racer Suzuki Yoshiko

64
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:26,640
is suspected of kidnapping and murder.

65
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:27,300
Therefore,

66
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,560
the Dragon Country Grand Prix organizing committee unanimously decided

67
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,560
to disqualify Suzuki Yoshiko from the race.

68
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,320
Furthermore,

69
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:34,320
they issued a notice to the racing community.

70
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,400
From now on,

71
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:38,360
no races or car companies are allowed to employ her.

72
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,160
That's great.

73
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,680
We have one less competitor.

74
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,079
Evil is rewarded with evil.

75
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:42,920
People like her

76
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,450
don't deserve to be racers.

77
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:47,010
Did you see that?

78
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:48,940
Serves them right.

79
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:49,720
Look.

80
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:52,840
Hello.

81
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:53,440
Lan.

82
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:54,760
Something will happen sooner or later.

83
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:55,560
That's right.

84
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,440
Lan.

85
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:09,680
What's up?

86
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,140
Can't I just call you for nothing?

87
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,839
I'm going abroad in a couple of days.

88
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,640
And I don't plan to come back.

89
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,400
So,

90
00:04:23,280 --> 00:04:25,280
do you want to go live abroad with me?

91
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,650
Forget about it.

92
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,040
I'm used to the freedom of being single.

93
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:31,570
I definitely won't get used to living abroad.

94
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:34,330
After everything that's happened recently,

95
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,560
I think I have fallen for you.

96
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,640
Lan,

97
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,840
do you really like me?

98
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,080
Yes.

99
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,840
I am in love with you.

100
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,240
So,

101
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,020
are you coming with me?

102
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,740
I already have someone I like.

103
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,240
Who?

104
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,120
Chen Ziqing?

105
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,370
I'm not telling you.

106
00:04:57,800 --> 00:05:00,200
Then when are you going to return the favor?

107
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:01,360
Except for giving myself to you,

108
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:03,020
you can ask for anything else.

109
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:06,090
Then take me to the top of Wutong Mountain tonight

110
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,020
to see the stars one more time.

111
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,020
No problem.

112
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:17,760
Lan,

113
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,840
I didn't agree to this.

114
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,480
Boring.

115
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:28,880
Sister.

116
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,360
You once taught me

117
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:34,400
to be someone who follows my heart.

118
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,690
No matter what happens,

119
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,120
as long as I like it,

120
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,880
I should bravely love

121
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,000
and pursue it,

122
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,890
leaving no regrets.

123
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,620
Hello, Sister Lan.

124
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,480
Ziqing,

125
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,260
I asked around for you.

126
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,760
He Nan already has someone he likes.

127
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,240
Did he say who it is?

128
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,200
No.

129
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:09,360
He wouldn't say.

130
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:11,560
Okay.

131
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:12,680
I got it.

132
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,610
You're welcome.

133
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:16,560
If you won't give up,

134
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,770
I suggest you ask him in person.

135
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,100
Thank you, Sister Lan.

136
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:42,880
He Nan.

137
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,360
Ziqing,

138
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,050
why are you here?

139
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:50,180
I heard you have someone you like.

140
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,720
I came to ask who it is.

141
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:53,890
How did you know?

142
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,770
Ye Lan told you, didn't she?

143
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:57,159
Never mind that.

144
00:06:58,080 --> 00:06:58,600
Anyway,

145
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,160
just tell me who it is.

146
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,730
I don't want to tell you.

147
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,320
Tell me.

148
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:09,880
If you don't tell me today,

149
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:10,940
I won't let you off.

150
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,760
You forced me to.

151
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,280
Don't be mad when I say it.

152
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:19,840
I won't be.

153
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,860
I'm not that petty.

154
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,200
This person,

155
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,160
she is...

156
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:33,159
Who?

157
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,480
She is...

158
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:36,440
Who? You...

159
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,770
You're messing with me.

160
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,530
Chen Ziqing.

161
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,770
I'm serious.

162
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:58,520
Ziqing,

163
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,540
if you're willing to put this back on,

164
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,880
I can change for you

165
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,580
and start over.

166
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,640
I do.

167
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,920
I do.

168
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,280
It's tied.

169
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,280
No going back.

170
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:20,760
Okay.

171
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:29,880
Tell me,

172
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,240
how many kids should we have?

173
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,159
In your dreams.

174
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,200
Ladies and gentlemen,

175
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,320
welcome to this year's

176
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,120
most exciting,

177
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:44,920
most thrilling,

178
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,200
and most spectacular Dragon Country Grand Prix

179
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,200
Annual Champion Ultimate Challenge!

180
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,040
Competing today

181
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:49,920
are TG Racing's pacemaker, He Nan,

182
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:51,580
and his partner, Chen Ziqing.

183
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,720
Today, they will take on the ultimate challenge

184
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,380
for the annual championship.

185
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:58,000
He Nan,

186
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,770
you have to do your best.

187
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,560
When I win the championship,

188
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:04,040
I'll propose to you

189
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,200
in front of the whole audience.

190
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:07,730
Maybe I'll be the one to win the championship.

191
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:11,520
The race begins!

192
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,520
Please stand.
